html:
Method

Method description

getIsEnabled()

Checks whether the custom feature is disabled. Retrieves the feature code. The business logic to execute depends on the retrieved value.

getIsDisabled()

Checks whether the custom feature is disabled. Retrieves the feature name. The business logic to execute depends on the retrieved value.
